50|$|Greidanus is {{best known}} for his {{emphasis}} on <b>preaching</b> Christ from Old Testament texts. He outlined his method for doing this in <b>Preaching</b> Christ from the Old Testament (1999) and followed this up with <b>Preaching</b> Christ from Genesis (2007), <b>Preaching</b> Christ from Ecclesiastes (2010), and <b>Preaching</b> Christ from Daniel (2012). His newest work in the series, <b>Preaching</b> Christ from the Psalms, came out in September 2016.|$|R
